<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Apr 2022 08:12:49 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>上海封城用無人機作廣播，籲市民勿開窗唱歌傳播病毒</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/08/shanghaiblockade/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=shanghaiblockade</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 08 Apr 2022 08:12:49 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[健康]]></category><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[COVID-19]]></category><category><![CDATA[上海封城]]></category><category><![CDATA[無人機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1094809</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近日中國上海 COVID-19 疫情再度爆發，政府隨即實施封城。而網上流傳影片，疑似上海公安在松江九亭小區以無 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">近日中國上海 COVID-19 疫情再度爆發，政府隨即實施封城。而網上流傳影片，疑似上海公安在松江九亭小區以無人機進行廣播，呼籲市民勿開窗唱歌，以免傳播病毒。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_31667"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0_GDKUKIaEs?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在當地居民拍攝的片段中，可聽到無人機廣播呼籲市民遵守規則，「控制靈魂對自由的渴望，不要開窗唱歌，此舉會有疫情傳播的風險。」</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而內地微博上，當地網民卻留言指出事實的另一面。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1094814" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/php5hoqkp-e1649397520488-694x425.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="425" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/php5hoqkp-e1649397520488-694x425.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/php5hoqkp-e1649397520488-768x470.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/php5hoqkp-e1649397520488.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">有網民留言指該區居民是自己的同學，他們並非唱歌，而是開窗呼喊沒有物資，致電求助沒有得到回覆；當地居委會更指四周物資站皆已關閉，無法派發物資，讓居民自行解決沒有物資的問題。更有網民回覆指聽到有人呼喊「快要餓死」。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">亦有網民指，事件過後政府便對發生呼喊事件的幾個小區，連夜發放物資。</span></p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3884721">自由時報</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
